---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | The House of the Eternal Flame">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-cinzel text-4xl text-center mb-8">About The Lucent Path</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-cinzel text-2xl mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="font-cormorant text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The House of the Eternal Flame serves as a sanctuary for those seeking spiritual enlightenment through The Lucent Path. 
            We believe in the transformative power of inner light and its ability to guide us through life's journey.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-cinzel text-2xl mb-4">Our Beliefs</h2>
          <ul class="font-cormorant text-gray-600 space-y-4">
            <li>• The eternal flame represents the divine light within each soul</li>
            <li>• Every individual has the potential to achieve spiritual enlightenment</li>
            <li>• Community and shared wisdom strengthen our spiritual journey</li>
            <li>• Sacred ceremonies help us connect with the divine</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="font-cinzel text-2xl mb-4">Our Minister</h2>
          <p class="font-cormorant text-gray-600 mb-4">
            As an ordained minister, I am dedicated to guiding others on their spiritual journey through The Lucent Path. 
            With expertise in performing weddings, baptisms, counseling, and funeral services, I am here to support our 
            community in all of life's sacred moments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>